subject: quote layer parse test
text:
Please quote 75 sets of 1.7# white Polyethylene foam.

The foam is made up of (3) layers, each 12" x 10".

Layer 1 (bottom):
Thickness 1.00"
No cavities.

Layer 2 (middle):
Thickness 2.50"
Includes 3 cavities:
- One rectangular cavity: 4.0" x 3.0" x 1.25" deep
- One rounded-corner cavity: 3.5" x 2.5" x 1.00" deep, 0.50" corner radius
- One circular cavity: Ø2.25" x 1.50" deep

Layer 3 (top):
Thickness 0.75"
Includes 1 circular through-hole: Ø1.50"

Please include pricing for the full foam set. Thank you.
